sketch.compiler.passes.lowering

Class EliminateImmutableStructs

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FEReplacer
      • sketch.compiler.passes.lowering.SymbolTableVisitor
        • sketch.compiler.passes.lowering.EliminateImmutableStructs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor

    public class EliminateImmutableStructs
extends SymbolTableVisitor
    This class replaces immutable structs with tuples. Converts constructors to tuple creates and field accesses to tuple reads.
